/target
# The demo/verify binaries load weights from ./models (fetched out-of-band).
# Vendored into semantra; the app itself loads models from src-tauri/models.
/models
# Library crate: its lockfile is not authoritative (the app's
# src-tauri/Cargo.lock resolves the full tree). Avoid committing a stray lock
# that can drift — e.g. one written by an incidental `cargo metadata` run.
/Cargo.lock
